### Obtener todos los clientes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/clientes

### Obtener cliente por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/clientes/1

### Crear nuevo cliente
POST http://localhost:3000/api/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Pedro",
    "apellido": "Martínez",
    "telefono": "3514567890",
    "email": "pedro.martinez@email.com",
    "dni": "22334455"
}

### Modificar cliente (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Juan Carlos",
    "apellido": "Pérez",
    "telefono": "3512345678",
    "email": "juancarlos.perez@email.com",
    "dni": "12345678"
}

### Modificar cliente (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "telefono": "3519999999",
    "email": "nuevo.email@email.com"
}

### Eliminar cliente
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/clientes/1
